recently_watched.Description: The Ranch follows the misadventures of the Bennett family as they navigate the ups and downs of running a ranch in Colorado. Filled with laughter, love, and plenty of drama, the series explores the complexities of family dynamics and the challenges of rural life in the modern West. With its blend of humor and heart, The Ranch offers a heartfelt portrayal of life on the ranch, reminding viewers that sometimes the most valuable lessons are learned close to home.

The Club is a Spanish drama series set in a prestigious gentlemens club in 1900s Madrid, where the members dark secrets, forbidden love affairs, and power struggles come to light amidst the backdrop of a changing society.
